description: Lists information about requested configured audience model associations.

parameters.name: membershipIdentifier
parameters.description: A unique identifier for a membership that contains the configured audience model associations that you want to retrieve.

nested_items.name: configuredAudienceModelAssociationSummaries
nested_items.description: Summaries of the configured audience model associations that you requested.

nested_items.name: membershipId
nested_items.description: A unique identifier of the membership that contains the configured audience model association.

nested_items.name: membershipArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the membership that contains the configured audience model association.

nested_items.name: collaborationArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the collaboration that contains the configured audience model association.

nested_items.name: collaborationId
nested_items.description: A unique identifier of the collaboration that configured audience model is associated with.

nested_items.name: createTime
nested_items.description: The time at which the configured audience model association was created.

nested_items.name: updateTime
nested_items.description: The most recent time at which the configured audience model association was updated.

nested_items.name: id
nested_items.description: A unique identifier of the configured audience model association.

nested_items.name: arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the configured audience model association.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The name of the configured audience model association.

nested_items.name: configuredAudienceModelArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the configured audience model that was used for this configured audience model association.

nested_items.name: description
nested_items.description: The description of the configured audience model association.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: The token value provided to access the next page of results.
